Titolo: Sakura Beach 2

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Sakura Beach 2 is a 2015 visual novel by British indie developer Winged Cloud. The game was released on 9 July 2014 on Steam as a sequel to the original Sakura Beach. Like Sakura Spiritâ€” It is one of the few visual novels that are developed outside Japan and aimed at the English-speaking market. It is also one of the first projects published by Sekai Project that is not a translation of a Japanese visual novel, but rather an original English work.
The game is a visual novel where the player reads text on the screen combined with anime-styled artwork. The game also gives the player the ability to make selections which further change the path the novel takes.

